		    <p>In regards to the color trasferring-With the brand that I used I actually slept on my hair and It did not transfer. This maybe different though with other brands or in a humid situation. Let me know how it turns out.<br />
In regards to use based pastels- Soft pastels tend to work<br />
Better because they have a higher portion of pigment making the color brighter and they tend to sick better to the hair.</p>

